# Ignore everything by default
*

# Track config and skills
!.gitignore
!CLAUDE.md
!settings.json
!statusline-command.sh
# skills/ mixes real dirs (committed) with machine-local symlinks into
# ~/.agents/skills — those break on any other clone, so ignore everything under
# skills/ by default and whitelist only the real skill dirs we want tracked.
!skills/
!skills/cmux/
!skills/cmux/**
!commands/
!commands/**
!hooks/
!hooks/**
!agents/
!agents/**
